Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:40.70,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}So, are the days no sweeter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.75,0:01:43.54,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}I got 'em on their knees
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:46.55,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Rotten to the core deeper, I couldn't hate them more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:50.78,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}I have reawakened for revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.83,0:01:54.68,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}All these petty rules won't stop me now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:56.53,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}They chew up and spit you out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:58.34,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Statue will leave a body count
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.39,0:02:00.25,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}But I'm getting stronger every day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:02.05,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Life is now a game I like to play
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:03.99,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}I give back the light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:05.99,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}It gimme what I please
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.80,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Like the Ring of Gyges
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:10.00,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Cuz I'm back in this game
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.05,0:02:11.86,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:15.56,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Dya know I could be the star of the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:17.48,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Cuz I'm back in this game
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:19.32,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}We can survive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:23.09,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}And nothing will crush this hunter's pride
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.14,0:02:26.64,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}The pain inside us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:27.23,op en,tag,0,0,18,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Trillion and one G on a bungee all stan
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.97,0:02:29.81,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Should never go away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:30.56,op en,tag,0,0,18,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Swelling my crescendo see a window
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.68,0:02:33.81,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Despite the violence
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:34.69,op en,tag,0,0,18,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}My miraculous story began provin' it to plato that I won't go shallow
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.48,0:02:37.96,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Shall never run away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:37.94,op en,tag,0,0,18,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Gonna be a player super slayer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:40.00,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Cuz I'm back in this game
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:41.83,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:45.49,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Dya know I could be the star of the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:47.41,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}Cuz I'm back in this game
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:49.09,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}We can survive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:52.92,op en,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur1}And nothing will crush this hunter's pride
